<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-4 pt-5">
            <div class="card_shadow rounded" style="height: 25vh;">
                <div class="overlap mt-5 row">
                    <div class="img-container rounded-circle mx-auto">
                        <img src="{{user.profilePic}}" alt="" id="profile-pic-wrapper"
                            class="rounded-circle shadow-dark overlay-img">
                        <div class="img-overlay">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-end" style="min-height: 23vh;">
                                <a type="button" onclick="opnUpdateWindow(event, '{{user.profilePic}}')" class="btn btn-info btn-sm rounded-pill px-3">Update</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body overlap">
                    <h4 class="text-primary text-center mt-2">{{user.name}} </h4>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card_shadow rounded mt-5">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="border-bottom py-2">
                        <a href="/my-orders" class="text-info">
                            <h6 class="text-uppercase pill_enlarge px-3 py-1">
                                <i class="fa fa-ticket mr-3"></i> My Orders
                            </h6>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="border-bottom py-2">
                        <a type="button" onclick="logout(event, '/logout')" class="text-info">
                            <h6 class="text-uppercase pill_enlarge px-3 py-1">
                                <i class="fa fa-power-off mr-3"></i> Logout
                            </h6>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <div class="card_shadow rounded">
                <div class="card-body" id="personal-info">
                    <div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <h5 class="ml-3">Personal Information</h5>
                            <a role="button" id="edit-personal-info"
                                class="text-decoration-none text-info font-weight-bold ml-4">Edit</a>
                            <a role="button" id="cancel-personal-info" hidden
                                class="text-decoration-none text-info font-weight-bold ml-4">Cancel</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="py-3 mb-3 border-bottom">
                            <form class="form-inline" id="edit-personal-info-form">
                                <input id="input-personal-info" class="form-control form-control-sm mr-sm-2" type="text"
                                    value="{{user.name}}" name="name" required readonly>
                                <select id="selectGender" class="custom-select custom-select-sm mr-sm-2" disabled>
                                    {{#if user.gender}}
                                    <option value="Male">Male</option>
                                    <option value="Female">Female</option>
                                    {{else}}
                                    <option value="" hidden>Gender</option>
                                    <option value="Male">Male</option>
                                    <option value="Female">Female</option>
                                    {{/if}}
                                </select>
                                <button id="save-personal-info"
                                    class="btn btn btn-outline-info rounded-pill px-5 my-2 my-sm-0" type="submit"
                                    onclick="editPersonalInfo('edit-personal-info-form')" hidden>Save</button>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <h5 class="ml-3">Email Address</h5>
                            <a role="button" id="edit-email"
                                class="text-decoration-none text-info font-weight-bold ml-4">Edit</a>
                            <a role="button" id="cancel-email" hidden
                                class="text-decoration-none text-info font-weight-bold ml-4">Cancel</a>
                            <a type="button" class="text-decoration-none text-info font-weight-bold ml-4"
                                data-toggle="modal" data-target="#changePassword">Change
                                Password</a>
                            <div class="modal fade" id="changePassword" data-backdrop="static" data-keyboard="false"
                                tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="changePasswordLabel" aria-hidden="true">
                                <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
                                    <div class="modal-content">
                                        <div class="modal-header">
                                            <h5 class="modal-title text-primary" id="changePasswordLabel">
                                                Change Password
                                            </h5>
                                            <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                                                <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                                            </button>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="modal-body">
                                            <div class="alert alert-info alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert"
                                                id="password-change-alert" hidden>
                                                <strong class="text-success" id="password-change-alert-body"></strong>
                                                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert"
                                                    aria-label="Close">
                                                    <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                                                </button>
                                            </div>
                                            <form id="change-password-form">
                                                <div class="form-group">
                                                    <label for="Input-current-password">Current password</label>
                                                    <input type="password" required name="currentPassword"
                                                        class="form-control" id="Input-current-password">
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="form-group">
                                                    <label for="Input-new-password">New password</label>
                                                    <input type="password" required name="newPassword"
                                                        class="form-control" id="Input-new-password">
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="form-group">
                                                    <label for="Input-confirm-password">Confirm new
                                                        password</label>
                                                    <input type="password" required name="confirmPassword"
                                                        class="form-control" id="Input-confirm-password">
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="row">
                                                    <button type="submit"
                                                        class="btn btn-primary rounded-pill px-5 ml-auto mr-3">Submit</button>
                                                </div>
                                            </form>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="py-3 mb-3 border-bottom">
                            <form class="form-inline" id="edit-email-form">
                                <input id="input-email" class="form-control form-control-sm mr-sm-2" type="email"
                                    value="{{user.email}}" name="email" required readonly>
                                <button id="save-email" class="btn btn btn-outline-info rounded-pill px-5 my-2 my-sm-0"
                                    type="submit" onclick="editPersonalInfo('edit-email-form')" hidden>Save</button>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <h5 class="ml-3">Mobile Number</h5>
                            <a role="button" id="edit-mobile"
                                class="text-decoration-none text-info font-weight-bold ml-4">Edit</a>
                            <a role="button" id="cancel-mobile" hidden
                                class="text-decoration-none text-info font-weight-bold ml-4">Cancel</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="py-3 mb-3 border-bottom">
                            <form class="form-inline" id="edit-mobile-form">
                                <input id="input-mobile" class="form-control form-control-sm mr-sm-2" type="text"
                                    value="{{user.mobileNumber}}" name="mobile" required readonly>
                                <button id="save-mobile" class="btn btn btn-outline-info rounded-pill px-5 my-2 my-sm-0"
                                    type="submit" onclick="editPersonalInfo('edit-mobile-form')" hidden>Save</button>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h5 class="mb-3">FAQs</h5>
                            <div>
                                <h6 class="mb-2">What happens when I update my email address (or mobile number)?</h6>
                                <p>Your login email id (or mobile number) changes, likewise. You'll receive all
                                    your
                                    account related communication on your updated email address (or mobile
                                    number).
                                </p>
                                <h6 class="my-2">When will my EasyCart account be updated with the new email address (or
                                    mobile
                                    number)?</h6>
                                <p>It happens as soon as you confirm the verification code sent to your email
                                    (or
                                    mobile) and save the changes.</p>
                                <h6 class="my-2">What happens to my existing EasyCart account when I update my email
                                    address
                                    (or
                                    mobile number)?</h6>
                                <p>Updating your email address (or mobile number) doesn't invalidate your
                                    account.
                                    Your account remains fully functional. You'll continue seeing your Order
                                    history, saved information and personal details.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>